{"tid":1854741,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"今日係思捷大師執導既首部親情笑中帶淚賀歲片《一家大晒》上映兩週年紀念！！！！！","createTime":"2020-01-31T16:01:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T12:54:42.000Z","uid":46435,"like":7,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0ee84d2a236a66e230be528c45357f7f44e6265a","tid":1854741,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:01:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5wmHJWx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5wmHJWx.jpg&h=87244062&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一家大晒&amp;nbsp;(Staycation)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">導演：李思捷</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">領銜主演：李思捷</span></span><br />\n主演：蘇玉華、狄龍、錢小豪、林敏驄、元秋、廖偉雄、羅家英<br />\n香港上映日期：2018年2月1日<br />\n預告：<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/e34auUjNmcY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fe34auUjNmcY&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMVKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=fcfc9e28\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/e34auUjNmcY</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n簡介：低端人口打工仔武德輝（李思捷飾）費盡心思安排一家四口與父親（狄龍飾）、母親（元秋飾）一家人去度假，想仔女棄打手機和自己多溝通同時，又想舊地重遊氹愛妻。&amp;nbsp;<br />\n豈料接二連三遭到神經刀大哥（林敏驄飾）核武級破壞，更有怪誕管理員（羅家英飾）全程瘋狂變臉招待，再加上思疑老婆（蘇玉華飾）疑似回春偷食，令他經歷一次三天兩夜妻離子散闔家歡非強迫購物無定向失常旅行團。<br />\n<br />\n唔知各位手足有咩想同思捷大師講呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今個新年上果幾套賀歲片全部咁垃圾 最岩就留係屋企同屋企人一齊睇一家大晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd1b8737a996aee441879e1a8146d192bb9df152","tid":1854741,"uid":136738,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:01:57.000Z","msg":"屌打左乜代宗師"},{"pid":"6750f317c9e46873f2bbbc81d4c13fc55e89620e","tid":1854741,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:08:06.000Z","msg":"過曬年先上不如清明上呀笨"},{"pid":"f9a42e1e4f695d86bca699ad02181b913485df9b","tid":185474